# 🎨 Color Palette Generator

A beautiful, fully functional color palette generator built as a trial task for **Digital Heroes**.

## ✨ Features

- **7 Color Harmony Modes**: Random, Complementary, Analogous, Triadic, Split-Complementary, Tetradic, Monochromatic
- **Lock Colors**: Keep your favorite colors while generating new palettes
- **Save Palettes**: Persist your favorite palettes in localStorage
- **Export Options**: JSON, CSS Variables, Tailwind Config
- **Image Color Extraction**: Upload any image to extract dominant colors
- **Dark/Light Mode**: Toggle between themes
- **Keyboard Shortcut**: Press `Spacebar` to generate new palette
- **Copy to Clipboard**: Click any color to copy its HEX code

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Custom Properties, Grid, Flexbox, Animations)
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+ Classes)
- Canvas API for image processing

